description: Returns a list of SLOs created in this account.

parameters.name: KeyAttributes
parameters.description: You can use this optional field to specify which services you want to retrieve SLO information for. This is a string-to-string map. It can include the following fields. Type designates the type of object this is. ResourceType specifies the type of the resource. This field is used only when the value of the Type field is Resource or AWS::Resource. Name specifies the name of the object. This is used only if the value of the Type field is Service, RemoteService, or AWS::Service. Identifier identifies the resource objects of this resource. This is used only if the value of the Type field is Resource or AWS::Resource. Environment specifies the location where this object is hosted, or what it belongs to. (string) --- (string) ---

parameters.name: DependencyConfig
parameters.description: Identifies the dependency using the DependencyKeyAttributes and DependencyOperationName. This is a string-to-string map. It can include the following fields. Type designates the type of object this is. ResourceType specifies the type of the resource. This field is used only when the value of the Type field is Resource or AWS::Resource. Name specifies the name of the object. This is used only if the value of the Type field is Service, RemoteService, or AWS::Service. Identifier identifies the resource objects of this resource. This is used only if the value of the Type field is Resource or AWS::Resource. Environment specifies the location where this object is hosted, or what it belongs to. (string) --- (string) --- The name of the called operation in the dependency.

nested_items.name: CreatedTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that this service level objective was created. It is expressed as the number of milliseconds since Jan 1, 1970 00:00:00 UTC.

nested_items.description: Displays whether this is a period-based SLO or a request-based SLO.

nested_items.description: Displays the SLI metric source type for this SLO. Supported types are:
Service operation.
Service dependency.
CloudWatch metric.
